    <string name="app_name">Hunting Log Helper</string>

    <string name="welcome_text">
        "Welcome!\n"
        "This app was created to assist in keeping up with the monsters needed to complete the various hunting logs in FFXIV."
        "The logs have been organized by class (Archer, Conjurer, etc), rank (1 - 5), the region/area in which to find"
        "the monsters (South Shroud - Upper Paths), the monster name (Diseased Treant, Earth Sprite, etc), the amount of the monsters"
        "needed to complete the log, and finally the x and y loc (x22,y22).\n"
        "It was done in this fashion to allow the player to quickly locate all needed monsters in a region/area, before moving on to a"
        "new location, without having to waste Gil or time teleporting back and forth.  Unfortunetly, there is no exact coordinates"
        "given for monsters needed inside of dungeons, only the dungeon locations are given."
    </string>
